    <!DOCTYPE html>
    <html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>Claim Submitted</title>
        <style>
            body {
                font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
                line-height: 1.6;
                color: #333;
                background-color: #f4f4f4;
                margin: 0;
                padding: 0;
            }
            .container {
                max-width: 600px;
                margin: 20px auto;
                padding: 20px;
                background-color: #fff;
                border-radius: 5px;
                box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            }
            h1 {
                color: #2C3E50; /* Deep blue */
                text-align: center;
                font-size: 24px;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }
            p {
                margin-bottom: 20px;
                line-height: 1.4;
                font-size: 16px;
            }
            a {
                color: #007bff;
                text-decoration: none;
            }
            a:hover {
                text-decoration: underline;
            }
            .footer {
                margin-top: 20px;
                text-align: center;
                color: #888;
                font-size: 14px;
            }
            .claim-details {
                background-color: #f8f8f8;
                padding: 15px;
                border-radius: 5px;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }
            .claim-details p {
                margin: 0;
                color: #4F4F4F; /* Dark gray */
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="container">
            <h1>New Claim Submitted</h1>
            <p>Dear Team,</p>
            <p>A new claim has been submitted on the TourJoy platform. Please find the details below:</p>
            <div class="claim-details">
                <p><strong>Title:</strong> {{ title }}</p>
                <p><strong>Description:</strong> {{ description }}</p>
            </div>
            <p>Thank you for your attention to this matter.</p>
            <p>Best regards,<br>TourJoy Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            &copy; {{ 'now'|date('Y') }} TourJoy. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </body>
    </html>
